message.entry: Trailing input arguments must occur in name-value pairs.
X and Y must be both tall arrays or both in-memory arrays.
XLimits must be a two-element sorted and finite array and must have the same class as X data.
YLimits must be a two-element sorted and finite array and must have the same class as Y data.
Tall inputs must be real column vectors.
When ''NumBinsMode'' is set to ''auto'', ''NumBins'' cannot be set.
When ''XLimitsMode'' is set to ''auto'', ''XLimits'' cannot be set.
When ''YLimitsMode'' is set to ''auto'', ''YLimits'' cannot be set.
When ''NumBinsMode'' is set to ''manual'', ''NumBins'' must be set.
When ''XLimitsMode'' is set to ''manual'', ''XLimits'' must be set.
When ''YLimitsMode'' is set to ''manual'', ''YLimits'' must be set.
